    },
    "Thank you for your support! After completing the payment, you’ll unlock the ability to play more music from the list and access additional settings." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "感谢您的支持！完成付款后，您将解锁更多列表中的音乐播放功能，并可访问更多设置选项。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Theme" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "主题"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This records paths and permissions. Individual music files are recorded separately. When a folder containing them is added, the file records are removed since they can be accessed via the folder." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "这里记录的是路径和权限。若列表中是单个音乐文件，会单独记录。添加包含这些文件的文件夹时，会清除原来的文件记录，因为已可通过文件夹访问。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
